Package com.rhizospherejs.gwt.client.renderer

Classes and interfaces for the generation and management of Rhizosphere renderings, that is, visual representation of Rhizosphere models.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
HasCacheDimensions Interface for RhizosphereRenderer instances to declare whether their renderings' dimensions can be cached or not.
HasChangeStyle<T> Interface for RhizosphereRenderer instances to declare that their renderings can handle custom style changes.
HasCustomDragHandlers Interface for RhizosphereRenderer instances to declare that their renderings use custom drag handlers.
HasExpandable Interface for RhizosphereRenderer instances to declare whether their renderings support expanded (maximized) status.
HasExpandableByModel<T> Interface for RhizosphereRenderer instances to declare whether their renderings support expanded (maximized) status on a model by model basis.
HasLegend Deprecated. This interface is the porting of equivalent functionality in the Rhizosphere javascript library that is scheduled for rewrite (http://code.google.com/p/rhizosphere/issues/detail?id=120).
HasRescalable<T> Interface for RhizosphereRenderer instances to declare that their renderings can handle resizing.
RenderingOutput Helper interface that RhizosphereRenderer instances use to emit and customize the renderings they produce.
WidgetBridge Propagates events that originate in JSNI code and affect a Widget lifecycle back into GWT space, to avoid memory leaks.
 

Class Summary
HasLegend.Range Deprecated.  
NativeRenderer<T> Bridge renderer that translates rendering instructions from RhizosphereRenderer instances into a native JSNI renderer that the Rhizosphere javascript library can understand.
RenderingHints Rendering hints about the enviroment a Rhizosphere visualization is embedded into.
RenderingOutputImpl Default implementation for the RenderingOutput interface.
 

Package com.rhizospherejs.gwt.client.renderer Description

Classes and interfaces for the generation and management of Rhizosphere renderings, that is, visual representation of Rhizosphere models.
